<s> As of the spec: The DOMBuilder section has this description: Asynchronous DOMBuilder objects are expected to also implement the events::EventTarget interface so that event listeners can be registered on asynchronous DOMBuilder objects.  </s>
<s> However, in order to implement the EventTarget interface, the DOMBuilder (which does NOT inherit from Node), needs the getFeature method.  </s>
<s> This will allow someone to go: DOMBuildermyBuilder; EventTargetmyTarget; myTarget = (EventTarget)myBuilder.getFeature("Events",  </s>
