<s> While I agree with you in practice, my feeling is that whole point behind the getFeature() method was to allow for implementions to have the flexibility in delegating DOM functionality to third-party code (See section 1.1.12.  </s>
<s> Mixed DOM implementations in the core spec).  </s>
<s> I feel that the specifications from the W3C should "eat-their-own-dog-food" so to speak.  </s>
<s> Therefore, we should not assume that the object implementing DOMBuilder must implement EventTarget.  </s>
<s> Therefore, you need a getFeature on DOMBuilder.  </s>
<s> If you feel that DOMBuilder *MUST* implement EventTarget, then change the definition of DOMBuilder to actually extend EventTarget.  </s>
<s> And yes, I do think that EventTarget should have a getFeature() method.  </s>
